### Verification

Release archives are checksummed. To verify a downloaded artifact:

```bash
sha256sum -c checksums.txt
```

The `checksums.txt` file is signed with keyless Sigstore when the GitHub release workflow publishes artifacts:

```bash
cosign verify-blob \
  --signature checksums.txt.sig \
  --certificate checksums.txt.pem \
  checksums.txt
```

